OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FJapanese snack maker Calbee has said
OL,8,Fit will change its colourful crisp
OL,9,Fpackaging to greyscale due to supply
OL,10,Fchain disruptions caused by the Iran
OL,11,Fwar.
OL,13,FImages released by Calbee show the new
OL,14,Fbags in varying shades of grey, with
OL,15,Fthe usual hat-wearing mascot, "Potato
OL,16,FBoy", nowhere to be seen ` leaving
OL,17,Fjust monochrome packaging and text
OL,18,Flabels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FCalbee said the temporary measure was
OL,8,Fin response to "supply instability
OL,9,Faffecting certain raw materials amid
OL,10,Fongoing tensions in the Middle East".
OL,12,F"This measure is intended to help
OL,13,Fmaintain a stable supply of products,"
OL,14,Fthe company said in a statement on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FCalbee did not specify exactly which
OL,18,Fshortages had prompted the change,
OL,19,Fwhich will be applied to 14 products
OL,20,Ffrom May 25.
OL,26,@pD@POUrD@dO]tD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FNaphtha, a petroleum byproduct, is
OL,8,Fsometimes used in parts of the ink
OL,9,Fmanufacturing process, and Japan
OL,10,Frelies on the Middle East for about
OL,11,F40% of its naphtha consumption,
OL,12,Faccording to the Japan Times.
OL,14,FThe newspaper also reported that 40%
OL,15,Fof domestically produced naphtha is
OL,16,Frefined from crude oil from the Middle
OL,17,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FHowever, a spokesman from the Japanese
OL,8,Fgovernment said it had "received no
OL,9,Freports of immediate supply issues
OL,10,Fregarding printing ink or naphtha".
OL,12,F"We recognise that the necessary
OL,13,Fvolume for Japan as a whole is being
OL,14,Fsecured," he added.
OL,16,FThe spokesperson added that the
OL,17,Fgovernment plans to meet with Calbee
OL,18,Fto discuss the situation and resolve
OL,19,Fany supply imbalances.
OL,26,@pD@XOUtD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
