PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FCalbee says the change will not affect
OL,8,Fthe quality of its snacks ` but it
OL,9,Fwill mean shoppers will have to rely
OL,10,Fmore on words on the packets to tell
OL,11,Fwhat they're buying.
OL,13,FUsually, fans of Calbee's snacks would
OL,14,Fknow the red bag is for lightly salted
OL,15,Fcrisps, while the yellow packets with
OL,16,Fgreen labels are for seaweed flavour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
