OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FCompanies around the world have been
OL,8,Fscrambling to find solutions to supply
OL,9,Fdisruptions since the US and Israel
OL,10,Fattacked Iran on February 28 and
OL,11,Ftriggered a prolonged regional
OL,12,Fconflict.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
