CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FIn response to attacks, Iran imposed a
OL,8,Fnaval blockade of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,F` a crucial shipping channel through
OL,10,Fwhich about a fifth of the world's gas
OL,11,Fand oil passed before the war.
OL,13,FDisruption to shipping has led to
OL,14,Ffertiliser shortages across Asia and
OL,15,Fhas left Indian rice producers unable
OL,16,Fto export their produce to Middle East
OL,17,Fmarkets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
