FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778598676
OL,3,CJapan's Calbee colourful crisp packets
OL,4,Cturn monochrome amid Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FThere have been delays in consumer
OL,8,Fdeliveries around the world, since
OL,9,FMiddle Eastern airlines account for a
OL,10,Fmajor share of global air cargo
OL,11,Fcapacity.
OL,13,FThe war has been taking its toll on
OL,14,Fthe UK too, with chief secretary to
OL,15,Fthe prime minister Darren Jones
OL,16,Fwarning the impact on the economy
OL,17,Fcould last for eight to 12 months
OL,18,Fafter the conflict is resolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
